Meteor 1.12 upgrade

A. Must destroy vagrant enviornment and re-provision

AND

B. Must use the latest 1.12 branch of mofacts and DO the following:
    
    -Must install nodejs 12.x
        curl -sL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_12.x | sudo bash -
    
    -Must install meteor 1.12
        curl https://install.meteor.com/?release=1.12 | sh

OR

C. Upgrade from a current branch that doesn't include 1.12

    -Must install nodejs 12.x
        curl -sL https://deb.nodesource.com/setup_12.x | sudo bash -
    
    -Must install meteor 1.12
        curl https://install.meteor.com/?release=1.12 | sh
    
    -Must cleanup old permissions
        sudo chown -R $(whoami) ~/.npm

    -Must update npm packages and remove incompatible package
        sudo rm -rf package-lock.json node_modules
        sudo npm cache clean --force
        sudo npm i --unsafe-perm node-sass
        export NODE_TLS_REJECT_UNAUTHORIZED=0 meteor remove fourseven:scss
        meteor add fourseven:scss@4.12.0

    -Must upgrade project
        meteor update --release 1.12

    -Reinstall removed package
        



    
